#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.112:0.2"
msgid "11. Antavagga "
msgstr "11. Sides "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 112. Dutiyachandappahānasutta → dutiyachandarāgasuttaṃ (bj) | chandarāgi 2 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.112:0.3"
msgid "112. Dutiyachandappahānasutta "
msgstr "112. Giving Up Desire (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.162, sc1
msgctxt "sn22.112:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.112:1.2"
msgid "“Rūpe, bhikkhave, yo chando yo rāgo yā nandī yā taṇhā ye upayupādānā cetaso adhiṭṭhānābhinivesānusayā, te pajahatha. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, you should give up any desire, greed, relishing, and craving for form; and any attraction, grasping, mental fixation, insistence, and underlying tendencies. "

msgctxt "sn22.112:1.3"
msgid "Evaṃ taṃ rūpaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati ucchinnamūlaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "Thus that form will be given up, cut off at the root, made like a palm stump, obliterated, and unable to arise in the future. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.112:1.4"
msgid "vedanāya … "
msgstr "You should give up any desire, greed, relishing, and craving for feeling … "

msgctxt "sn22.112:1.5"
msgid "saññāya … "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "sn22.112:1.6"
msgid "saṅkhāresu yo chando … pe … "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "sn22.112:1.7"
msgid "evaṃ te saṅkhārā pahīnā bhavissanti ucchinnamūlā tālāvatthukatā anabhāvaṃkatā āyatiṃ anuppādadhammā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn22.112:1.8"
msgid "Viññāṇe yo chando yo rāgo yā nandī yā taṇhā ye upayupādānā cetaso adhiṭṭhānābhinivesānusayā, te pajahatha. "
msgstr "consciousness; and any attraction, grasping, mental fixation, insistence, and underlying tendencies. "

msgctxt "sn22.112:1.9"
msgid "Evaṃ taṃ viññāṇaṃ pahīnaṃ bhavissati ucchinnamūlaṃ tālāvatthukataṃ anabhāvaṃkataṃ āyatiṃ anuppādadhamman”ti. "
msgstr "Thus that consciousness will be given up, cut off at the root, made like a palm stump, obliterated, and unable to arise in the future.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.112:1.10"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.112:1.11"
msgid "Antavaggo paṭhamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn22.112:2.1"
msgid "Anto dukkhañca sakkāyo, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.112:2.2"
msgid "pariññeyyā samaṇā duve; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.112:2.3"
msgid "Sotāpanno arahā ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.112:2.4"
msgid "duve ca chandappahānāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
